variables.text: If you let go of run while performing a grab, rather than skidding you will go into the walking state instead and gradually lose your speed over time, this is referred to as a fastwalk. You can hold run again while fastwalking to transition right back into your mach run. In the following section, input a grab when you fall of the ledge and let go of run to slow yourself down, then right when you pass the line start holding run again to transition back to a mach run.

Since a fastwalk counts as being in a walking state you can avoid interacting with objects your mach run wouldn't. In the following section performing a jump grab to enter the fastwalk state, then walk past the Pizzaboy cutout and start running again.

When you reach the top of a wall Peppino will be put in the air right above the ground, this is referred to as a pop-up. If you input a grab right before or during this window and let go of your run button you can initiate a fastwalk. In the following section, try performing a fastwalk right when you reach the top of the wall to walk through the mach turnaround wall.
